parsed.explanation: Several encoding artifacts (`\u221a\u00fc`, `\u221a\u2202`, `\u221a\u2264`, `\u221a\u00a7`) were corrected to proper German umlauts (`ä`, `ö`, `ü`, `ß`) or format indicators (`°`, `vo`). Specifically, 'Augustinerga\u221a\u00fc' was fixed to 'Augustinergaß', 'V\u221a\u2202lcker' to 'Völker', 'B\u221a\u2202dickers' to 'Bödickers', and 'Grunds\u221a\u00a7tze' to 'Grundsätze'. The unprocessable separator '\u221a\u2020' was removed. The malformed tag `<PRIZE>` containing 'Cattenburg' was relabeled as `<COMMENT>`. Crucially, a missing closing `</BIBL>` tag was added after the second entry (`Sapientia Mos.`) to prevent improper nesting. Finally, the unescaped ampersand character (&) in the second title was converted to the XML entity `&`.
